The php framework.

A more complete module tutorial/guide/documentation will come at some point in future..

Features:

- Custom templates
- HTML Form builder                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
- Dynamic language support
- Module system


Module system:
Adding modules is easy as adding an entry to the database and copying the module to /modules folder. The module is accessed when the client hits certain url, like http://yourwebsite.me/mymodulename.